{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_24031.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1,"bg":"bg_adv_21251.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"exitWitchSpace","se":"7209_gate_close"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song05","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-1"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Perhaps the Tokime Clan of old knew about this."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102600,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-2"}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"About what?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-3"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"That humans are a mix of both good and evil,@but the goodness comes out in the end..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102500,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-4"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"So from behind the scenes they made wishes@and focused on defeating Devils,"},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-5"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"while watching over the people..."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-6"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I kind of understand it now."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-7"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Remaining uninvolved was evidence of@their belief in people's innate goodness."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-8"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"There was actually a specific inspiration@behind Miss Futaba's story."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-9"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Was it from some old tale?"},{"chara":[{"id":102700,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-10"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"No. The turtle is Sana herself, and the bird is Iroha."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-11"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...*Chuckle*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-12"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Now that you say it, it makes sense."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-13"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Deep down, I've actually been jealous of Iroha..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-14"}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Maybe you were subconsciously trying@to take a different path than Iroha,"},{"chara":[{"id":102600,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-15"}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"to find your own path as the leader of the clan."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-16"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"That might be..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter9/103004_tokime_persons.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Shizuka","narration":"―Shizuka―@I did something unforgivable@just when we were about to join hands...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":10,"narrationLineSpace":20,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-17"},{"narration":"―Shizuka―@And yet, I feel a sense of peace@that I can be forgiven,","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-18"},{"narration":"―Shizuka―@as though we're being carried@on the feelings that Iroha has nurtured.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-19"},{"nameNarration":"Chiharu","narration":"―Chiharu―@Even when the people of Kamihama were having a hard time,@they still reached out to Promised Blood.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-20"},{"nameNarration":"Sunao","narration":"―Sunao―@I feel that they don't have any@enmity against Miss Aika, either.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-21"},{"nameNarration":"Shizuka","narration":"―Shizuka―@Iroha has never had any desire@to fight from the very start.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-22"},{"narration":"―Shizuka―@She knows that we're all suffering, even me,@and that we all wanted to be saved.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-23"},{"narration":"―Shizuka―@She's looking for a way to save everyone...@I'm sure of it.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-24"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21131.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":304700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102500,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-25"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Ah...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.1},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-26"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Are we back...?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":304700,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-27"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":1,"nameRight":"Chika","textRight":"Thank goodness you woke up safely.@How are you doing?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":304700}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-28","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-27"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":0,"nameRight":"Ryoko","textRight":"Chiharu and Sunao both woke up just fine,@so you know."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-29"}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"Yes, sorry for the trouble."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-30"}],"nameLeft":"Chiharu","textLeft":"No problems here!"},{"chara":[{"id":305800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-31"}],"nameRight":"Ryoko","textRight":"The most important thing is, how is our big chief?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102500,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-32"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-33"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I know this is late, but I've@finally come to my senses..."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-34"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I'm ashamed of the baseless confidence@I had that I was doing good..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-35"}],"nameRight":"Ryoko","textRight":"That's good to hear."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":305800,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-36"}],"nameRight":"Ryoko","textRight":"Sorry about everything, Shizuka.@From now on, I'll support you too."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":304700,"motion":200,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-37"}],"nameRight":"Chika","textRight":"As a fellow member of the Tokime Clan,@please let me support you as well."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-38"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Yeah, thank you both."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":304700}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-39"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuka","textCenter":"Now, without further ado,@let's head for the mountains."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-40"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuka","textCenter":"As you've already heard, the Neo-Magius are@trying to control people's ability to eat,"},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-41"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuka","textCenter":"and in doing so force the populace to fear them."},{"chara":[{"id":102500,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-42"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuka","textCenter":"I know that I'm in no position to speak,@but we must stop them no matter what."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102500}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-43_chiharu"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp3.json","id":305800,"motion":400,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-43_ryoko"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":304700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-43_chika"}],"nameCenter":"Everyone","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"Let's gooooooo!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":304700},{"effect":"fadeout","id":305800},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102600}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-44"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"But first, we need to purify your Soul Gem. It's@gotten all murky from what happened in the dream."},{"autoTurnLast":3,"chara":[{"effect":"ef_adv_09","id":102500}],"se":"7210_souljem_01","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102500,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-45"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Thank you. Let's keep up the good work."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102700,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-46"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Yes."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21501.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"surround":"7003_wind","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102001,"pos":0}]},{"chara":[{"id":820200,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Uwasa of the Wind Evangelist","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-48"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I see, so Miss Shizuka listened to those two."},{"chara":[{"id":820200,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Uwasa of the Wind Evangelist","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-50"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"That's right."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-51"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I hope we can all make a collective decision@and walk forward together."},{"chara":[{"id":820200,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Uwasa of the Wind Evangelist","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-53"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yeah, I'm happy for her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-54"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"While it's not the same as changing her@fate of becoming a Witch someday,"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-55"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"now Miss Shizuka has been freed@from the Tokime Clan's curse."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-56"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I think that's very encouraging, for a Magical@Girl to break free of what binds them,"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-57"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"and start moving forward."},{"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"Also, this event inspired at a time when@I was feeling hesitant about spreading@the truth of Magical Girls.","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","surround":"stop","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-58"},{"narration":"The Tokime Clan is an example of a group@that was taken advantage of by people@that knew about Magical Girls, but this felt@like they were able to rise above their past.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-59"},{"narration":"And more than anything, this time it wasn't just@the Tokime Clan working alone, but also@Miss Iroha and Miss Oba, who knew about the@situation and got involved to solve it together.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-60"},{"narration":"Yes, I think that knowing about someone's@situation allows you to show them kindness,@and that that's true for Magical Girls as well.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103004/vo_full_103004-13-61"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
